show.title: My Husband My Boss
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/3T44RG
show.description: Meher Verma enters a secret contract marriage to escape her toxic family—only to unknowingly cross paths with her mysterious husband two years later, as her new boss. In a world of ambition, hidden identities, and simmering tension, Meher must protect her heart and her secrets. But as sparks fly and buried truths threaten to surface, she’s forced to choose between love, loyalty, and freedom.
